article_title: Ukrainian band Okean Elzy sings for unity in capital Kiev
article_text: - The day after Ukraine declared a ceasefire 70,000 people enjoyed a concert by popular Ukrainian band Okean Elzy. The frontman’s message was that a united Ukraine can achieve anything. ()
